import React from "react";
import {
  Box, Grid, Card, Typography, Avatar, Button, Divider
} from "@mui/material";
import ShoppingCartIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ShoppingCart";
import WalletIcon from "@mui/icons-material/AccountBalanceWallet";
import StarIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Star";
import HistoryIcon from "@mui/icons-material/History";

const UserDashboard = () => (
  <Box sx={{ bgcolor: "#fff5f7", minHeight: "100vh", py: 4 }}>
    {/* Header */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        bgcolor: "#e23744",
        color: "#fff",
        py: 3,
        px: 4,
        borderRadius: 3,
        mb: 4,
        boxShadow: 2,
        display: "flex",
        alignItems: "center",
        justifyContent: "space-between"
      }}
    >
      <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
        <Avatar
          // User image or placeholder
          sx={{ width: 56, height: 56, bgcolor: "#fff", color: "#e23744", mr: 2 }}
        >
          U
        </Avatar>
        <Box>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={700}>
            Welcome, [User Name]!
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="subtitle1">
            Doorstep fuel delivery, made easy.
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
      <Button
        variant="contained"
        sx={{
          bgcolor: "#fff",
          color: "#e23744",
          fontWeight: 700,
          borderRadius: 99,
          '&:hover': { bgcolor: "#ffb0b9" }
        }}
      >
        My Account
      </Button>
    </Box>
    {/* Dashboard Cards */}
    <Grid container spacing={3}>
      {/* Loyalty */}
      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
            <StarIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="textSecondary" fontWeight={600}>
                Available Loyalty
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={800}>₹0</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
      {/* Wallet */}
      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
            <WalletIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="textSecondary" fontWeight={600}>
                My Wallet Limit
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={800}>₹0</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
      {/* Cart */}
      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
            <ShoppingCartIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 40, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="textSecondary" fontWeight={600}>
                Cart Status
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={800}>Active</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
    {/* Orders and Assets */}
    <Divider sx={{ my: 4 }} />
    <Grid container spacing={3}>
      {/* Last 5 Orders */}
      <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
        <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={800} mb={1}>
            My Last 5 Orders
          </Typography>
          <Divider sx={{ mb: 2 }} />
          {/* Map your order items here. Example: */}
          <Typography>No records found</Typography>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
      {/* Assets */}
      <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ p: 3, borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={800} mb={1}>
            My Assets
          </Typography>
          <Divider sx={{ mb: 2 }} />
          {/* Map user's assets here */}
          <Typography>No records found</Typography>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  </Box>
);

export default UserDashboard;
